description: Criteo is an advertising network that specializes in retargeting.  They provide pay-per-click, personalized, re-targeting solutions to e-tailers, content portals, community sites and advertising platforms. Criteo's technology enables advertisers to find potential customers who have left a website and re-engage them through dynamic banner ads generated in real-time.  Each ad contains relevant, product specific information determined on a user's previous visit to an e-commerce site.

